/MapLibre/MLNMultiPolygon/multiPolygonWithPolygons:":{"title":"multiPolygonWithPolygons:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"multiPolygonWithPolygons:"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolygon\/multipolygonwithpolygons:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Creates and returns a multipolygon object consisting of the given polygons."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon\/multiPolygonWithPolygons:","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPolygon":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolygon","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"polygons that do not overlap. For example, you could use a multipolygon shape"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to represent the body of land that consists of an island surrounded by an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"atoll: the inner island would be one "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object, while the surrounding"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"atoll would be another. You could also use a multipolygon shape to represent a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"group of disconnected but related buildings."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon","title":"MLNMultiPolygon","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMultiPolygon"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPolygon":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpolygon","role":"symbol","kind"